lade black\" /></figure>\n</div>\n                <div></div>\n        </div></figure>\n\n\n\n<figure><img width=\"800\" height=\"534\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Pivot-Switchblade-launch-2024-first-ride-review-photo-c-Jens-Staudt-72-800x534.jpg\" alt=\"Pivot Switchblade limited 35th Talon anniversary\n\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Pivot-Switchblade-launch-2024-first-ride-review-photo-c-Jens-Staudt-72-800x533.jpg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Pivot-Switchblade-launch-2024-first-ride-review-photo-c-Jens-Staudt-72-297x198.jpg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Pivot-Switchblade-launch-2024-first-ride-review-photo-c-Jens-Staudt-72-120x80.jpg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Pivot-Switchblade-launch-2024-first-ride-review-photo-c-Jens-Staudt-72-768x512.jpg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Pivot-Switchblade-launch-2024-first-ride-review-photo-c-Jens-Staudt-72-1536x1025.jpg 1536w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Pivot-Switchblade-launch-2024-first-ride-review-photo-c-Jens-Staudt-72-720x480.jpg 720w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Pivot-Switchblade-launch-2024-first-ride-review-photo-c-Jens-Staudt-72.jpg 2000w\" />\n\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\n\t\t        <div>\n                \n                    \n                \n                <div>\n<figure><img alt=\"Pivot Switchblade limited 35th Talon anniversary\n\" /></figure>\n</div>\n                <div>\n<figure><img alt=\"Pivot Switchblade limited 35th Talon anniversary\n\" /></figure>\n</div>\n                <div></div>\n        </div></figure>\n<figcaption>(Photos/Pivot)</figcaption></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Pricing starts at $6,399 for the Ride SLX/XT build, and tops out at $11,399 for the standard Team XX AXS Transmission build. There’s also a <a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/pink-switchblade-limited-edition-original-sun-eagle-talon-mtb/\" targe